= Document

Document is a simple gem for representing a document, used as a learning tool to get
the hang of doing gems.

== Installing

Document can be installed via RubyGems:

  gem install document

== Using Document

Document just holds an author, a title and some content:
  doc = Document.new( 'Eloquent Ruby', 'Russ Olsen', 'Some years ago...' )
  puts doc.title
  puts doc.author
  puts doc.content
